# ~/.config/yabai/yabairc 

# event hook for enabling the dock injection for spaces management
# must be before --load-sa
yabai -m signal --add event=dock_did_restart action="sudo yabai --load-sa"
sudo yabai --load-sa

yabai -m config                                 \
    window_placement          second_child    \
    window_gap                10              \
    top_padding               10              \
    bottom_padding            10              \
    right_padding             10              \
    left_padding              10              \
    layout                    bsp             \
    mouse_follows_focus       on              \
    mouse_modifier            alt             \
    mouse_action1             move            \
    mouse_action2             resize          \
    mouse_drop_action         swap

yabai -m space 1 --label personal --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 2 --label spotify --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 3 --label terminal --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 4 --label slack --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 5 --label tasks --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 6 --label figma --padding rel:0:0:0:0
yabai -m space 7 --label lower_monitor_main --padding rel:0:0:185:0

# left padding to bottom screen to show times, reminders, and crypto tickers on desktop
